00:31:36,466 --> 00:31:37,060
How?

543
00:31:37,513 --> 00:31:39,540
Mi is complaining.

544
00:31:41,893 --> 00:31:42,500
Dad.

545
00:31:42,500 --> 00:31:44,260
Since when are you here?

546
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,980
Dad, have you ever thought

547
00:31:48,386 --> 00:31:50,900
that maybe your daughter is not good for practising magics?

548
00:31:52,293 --> 00:31:53,020
Mi...

549
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,860
I ask you to practice

550
00:31:56,753 --> 00:31:58,900
not to make me proud.

551
00:31:59,926 --> 00:32:01,660
It's very hard.

552
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:03,460
But it can cultivate your temperament.

553
00:32:03,673 --> 00:32:05,100
I don’t want you

554
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,940
to become a greenhouse flower.

555
00:32:07,506 --> 00:32:09,900
Nowadays, I'm with you.

556
00:32:10,073 --> 00:32:11,700
You can depend on me.

557
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:14,020
But one day,

558
00:32:14,540 --> 00:32:17,540
I will disappear.

559
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:19,300
I can't protect you forever.

560
00:32:19,300 --> 00:32:20,140
Dad.

561
00:32:20,506 --> 00:32:21,700
Please don't say this.

562
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:23,100
I don't want to listen.

563
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:26,740
You have to go through many difficulties
and hardships to be successful.

564
00:32:26,740 --> 00:32:27,900
Only after experiencing

565
00:32:28,213 --> 00:32:31,300
difficulties and hardships can you get great achievements.

566
00:32:32,173 --> 00:32:33,580
What I ask you to cultivate

567
00:32:33,580 --> 00:32:35,580
is the ability to distinguish between right and wrong,

568
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:38,820
self-esteem, self-love and self-improvement

569
00:32:39,186 --> 00:32:42,140
In the future, you will walk between heaven and earth freely.

570
00:32:42,140 --> 00:32:43,980
You will have a clear conscience.

571
00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:46,700
You won’t bend over and lean over anyone.

572
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:50,860
I hope Mi you can understand my good intentions

573
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:52,220
in the future.

574
00:33:21,713 --> 00:33:23,380
What are you thinking?

575
00:33:25,486 --> 00:33:27,620
Some past events with Suifen.

576
00:33:32,340 --> 00:33:32,940
Lin Xiu.

577
00:33:34,226 --> 00:33:35,880
What kind of man do you like?

578
00:33:36,313 --> 00:33:37,820
I have never thought about these.

579
00:33:39,393 --> 00:33:40,740
Really?

580
00:33:41,033 --> 00:33:41,660
Really.

581
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:42,980
What should I lie to you?

582
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:45,520
Have you never thought about

583
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:47,620
what kind of man you would marry?

584
00:33:47,620 --> 00:33:49,420
with whom you want be together forever?

585
00:33:49,420 --> 00:33:51,980
I have the companion of you
and the senior fellow apprentice.

586
00:33:51,980 --> 00:33:52,940
It's enough.

587
00:33:53,333 --> 00:33:54,980
Then you like the senior fellow apprentice.

588
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:56,500
Don't talk nonsense.

589
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:59,460
the senior fellow apprentice is very handsome.

590
00:33:59,460 --> 00:34:02,750
There is almost no one in the Heaven Realm who can compare
with him in terms of appearance and brilliance.

591
00:34:02,750 --> 00:34:03,860
You don't like him?

592
00:34:04,806 --> 00:34:05,490
How about you?

593
00:34:06,246 --> 00:34:07,020
Do you like him?

594
00:34:08,660 --> 00:34:09,460
I don't know.

595
00:34:11,346 --> 00:34:12,700
Push me fast.

596
00:34:12,700 --> 00:34:14,380
Hurry up. Push me a little higher.

597
00:34:14,686 --> 00:34:15,700
I'm coming.

598
00:34:16,633 --> 00:34:17,580
Then you must be careful.

599
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:18,580
Don't fall over.

600
00:34:22,640 --> 00:34:23,820
Higher, higher.

601
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:24,450
Coming!

602
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:40,180
Zi Fen!

603
00:34:49,393 --> 00:34:50,620
I said before.

604
00:34:51,753 --> 00:34:54,700
The personalities of Mi and Zi Fen were different.

605
00:34:55,466 --> 00:34:56,780
But when thinking it over,

606
00:34:57,080 --> 00:34:58,540
I feel there are many similarities

607
00:34:58,540 --> 00:35:00,340
between them.

608
00:35:01,580 --> 00:35:04,460
I nearly forgot

609
00:35:05,433 --> 00:35:07,940
that Zi Fen occasionally played about very much.

610
00:35:08,953 --> 00:35:10,050
Time passes on quickly.

611
00:35:12,673 --> 00:35:14,540
It's a pity that Zi Fen died too early.

612
00:35:16,733 --> 00:35:17,660
Fortunately.

613
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:21,300
We still have these

614
00:35:24,093 --> 00:35:25,300
happy memories.

615
00:36:41,853 --> 00:36:43,320
I used to think innocently

616
00:36:43,993 --> 00:36:47,660
that we three can be together forever,

617
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,460
living a happy life.

618
00:36:51,260 --> 00:36:52,340
But fortunately,

619
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:54,740
she left Jin Mi to us.

620
00:36:56,480 --> 00:37:00,500
Everything is changing. For thousands of years,

621
00:37:01,706 --> 00:37:04,300
I have not fulfilled any responsibility of being a father.

622
00:37:05,333 --> 00:37:06,940
I really feel guilty for Mi.

623
00:37:13,586 --> 00:37:14,900
There's much time left.

624
00:37:15,413 --> 00:37:16,740
We still have a lot of time

625
00:37:16,740 --> 00:37:17,860
to accompany Mi.

626
00:37:19,226 --> 00:37:20,060
I believe

627
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:22,500
you are a good father.

628
00:37:23,286 --> 00:37:24,540
For my daughter

629
00:37:24,540 --> 00:37:26,260
I can do anything.

630
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:28,380
Tomorrow,

631
00:37:29,313 --> 00:37:32,440
I will take my Mi to see Master.

632
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:53,540
How does the green lotus lack a flap?

633
00:37:54,246 --> 00:37:54,900
Mi.

634
00:38:02,046 --> 00:38:03,260
Master.

635
00:38:03,260 --> 00:38:04,420
Immortal.

636
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:09,180
Stand up.

637
00:38:10,666 --> 00:38:11,660
Thanks, Master.

638
00:38:11,660 --> 00:38:12,660
Thanks, Immortal.

639
00:38:20,900 --> 00:38:24,220
So she is the daughter of you and Zi Fen.

640
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:25,580
Yes, she is.

641
00:38:27,406 --> 00:38:28,580
Master, please

642
00:38:29,693 --> 00:38:32,420
remove the Jialan seal on my daughter.

643
00:38:33,726 --> 00:38:34,820
I come here so suddenly.

644
00:38:34,820 --> 00:38:36,620
I hope Master can forgive me.

645
00:38:38,520 --> 00:38:41,340
It will be in vain.

646
00:38:44,266 --> 00:38:45,740
Can't the seal be removed?

647
00:38:45,826 --> 00:38:47,640
If so, I won't be able to improve my magic power.

648
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:49,060
Then what about Rou Rou?

649
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:50,620
Master, please give me clear explanation.

650
00:38:51,733 --> 00:38:53,220
For the one who is dying,

651
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:55,180
it doesn't matter

652
00:38:55,180 --> 00:38:59,100
whether the seal is removed or not.

653
00:38:59,520 --> 00:39:00,900
Master, you are compassionate,

654
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:03,140
saving the world in danger.

655
00:39:03,686 --> 00:39:04,380
I beg you.

656
00:39:04,540 --> 00:39:07,940
Please save my daughter's life.

657
00:39:08,066 --> 00:39:10,780
To save a life doesn't mean compassion.

658
00:39:11,606 --> 00:39:14,300
To save one hundred lives doesn't mean compassion.

659
00:39:14,786 --> 00:39:17,820
To save all beings does mean compassion.

660
00:39:18,313 --> 00:39:22,020
A tiger in the mountain that is seriously injured and dying.

661
00:39:22,020 --> 00:39:23,980
Save it or not?

662
00:39:24,226 --> 00:39:25,380
Of course, yes.

663
00:39:25,666 --> 00:39:27,740
The tiger recovers and comes back to the mountain,

664
00:39:27,740 --> 00:39:30,230
catching deer and eating weak rabbits.

665
00:39:30,973 --> 00:39:33,540
In this way, the result of saving a life
is to hurt hundreds of lives.

666
00:39:33,540 --> 00:39:35,180
Without witness, compassion

667
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:37,140
can hurt living beings.

668
00:39:38,220 --> 00:39:40,100
Jin Mi is pure and simple.

669
00:39:41,106 --> 00:39:42,460
She definitely will not hurt others.

670
00:39:42,460 --> 00:39:44,140
Please consider it, Master.

671
00:39:53,180 --> 00:39:54,700
As one of the Immortals in the six realms,

672
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:56,380
I am making a wish today.

673
00:39:56,786 --> 00:40:00,140
Master, please help Jin Mi survive this.

674
00:40:00,866 --> 00:40:03,300
Luo Lin will repay

675
00:40:03,300 --> 00:40:06,140
and help the beings in hardships

676
00:40:08,700 --> 00:40:11,380
To live doesn't mean being alive.

677
00:40:11,973 --> 00:40:14,900
To die doesn't mean being dead.

678
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:16,900
The appearance comes from the heart.

679
00:40:16,900 --> 00:40:20,540
Everything in the world is just outer shapes.

680
00:40:20,973 --> 00:40:24,220
When the heart does not feel, everything won't move.

681
00:40:24,953 --> 00:40:29,380
When heart remains unchanged, everything won't change.

682
00:40:30,500 --> 00:40:31,240
Jin Mi.

683
00:40:31,740 --> 00:40:32,980
Come here.

684
00:40:56,106 --> 00:41:00,580
Love produces worries and fears.

685
00:41:01,126 --> 00:41:05,340
Without love, you will be free from worries and fears.

686
00:41:07,340 --> 00:41:10,100
May this help you survive the hardship.

687
00:41:11,033 --> 00:41:12,060
Thank you, Immortal

688
00:41:15,873 --> 00:41:16,540
Immortal,

689
00:41:16,866 --> 00:41:17,460
I heard

690
00:41:17,460 --> 00:41:19,200
that you are the Great Immortal.

691
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:19,900
with strong magic power.

692
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:21,540
I have been looking for you for a long time.

693
00:41:21,786 --> 00:41:24,540
In order to see you, I practice hard every day.

694
00:41:24,540 --> 00:41:26,220
I have accumulated a lot of magic power.

695
00:41:26,706 --> 00:41:28,050
Can you do me a favor?

696
00:41:36,286 --> 00:41:37,580
This is my best friend.

697
00:41:37,766 --> 00:41:38,660
Her name is Rou Rou.

698
00:41:39,053 --> 00:41:40,740
Can you save her?

699
00:41:49,093 --> 00:41:50,840
You will soon meet each other.

700
00:41:51,286 --> 00:41:53,780
But you will say goodbye finally.

701
00:41:54,806 --> 00:41:55,500
Really?

702
00:41:56,833 --> 00:41:57,740
Thank you, Immortal

703
00:41:57,953 --> 00:42:00,100
As long as I can see her, I have nothing to ask for.

704
00:42:04,260 --> 00:42:05,340
My daughter is being rude.

705
00:42:05,340 --> 00:42:07,800
Master, please remove the seal on her.
